Summary: Taking pictures from my balcony I uploaded images and this thing appeared
divs: Sighting DetailsI often stand on my balcony to enjoy the weather and hope to catch glimpses of stars, sight the moon in phases, etc. I've been trying out my new camera and trying it on different settings and times of day and night. This particular night I took a series of pictures and on some I captured some odd images. This was one. After uploading them I saw many different strange objects on the images, this one was the most startling. I did not notice this object when I took the photograph.
